<subSubSection pageId="92" pageNumber="93" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="92.[700,1229,1278,1741]" pageId="92" pageNumber="93">DIAGNOSIS: The extraordinary, elongate pronotum (23:30) distinguishes the members of this species; the width across the eyes is greater than the width of the pronotum (23: 24); the frontal setal tuft and the metepisternal tuft are present.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
